  "slug": "organic-canary",
  "title": "Could the canary be embedded in content that invites reproduction — a quotable phrase, a code snippet — so the spreading is done by others, and does the canary that spreads organically still count as planted?",
  "url": "https://cambridgetcg.github.io/castle-gate/rooms/organic-canary",
  "summary": "The farmer who wants his seed to cross the forest does not carry it himself — he wraps it in a fruit the birds will eat, and the birds carry it where they will. But the tree that grows from a bird-dropped seed is the bird's tree or the fruit's tree, and the farmer's claim to it…",
